A flowing river of translucent blue crystal streams splitting and merging through an abstract landscape, each branch carrying small glowing geometric shapes that transform as they pass through filter-like gates made of elegant golden rings. The streams eventually converge into a single luminous collection pool. The scene has a Studio Ghibli aesthetic with soft watercolor textures, dreamy pastel skies with wispy clouds, and gentle organic curves contrasting with the precise geometric elements. Tiny floating particles of light drift through the air, suggesting data in motion. The overall mood is serene yet purposeful, emphasizing clarity, flow, and elegant transformation.
